data.description: Back on market as buyer financing fell through. Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 4 bath home located in the much sought after east school district. This spacious 1.5 story residence offers everything you need for comfortable and convenient living, including a garage, storage building, and a rear porch. The garage and storage building offer plenty of room for your vehicles, outdoor equipment, and additional storage space. Whether you have a hobby or need space for extra belongings, this home has you covered. Step outside onto the covered rear porch and enjoy the serenity and privacy of your backyard oasis. The porch is the perfect spot for enjoying your morning coffee or relaxing with a book in the evening, all while being protected from the elements. This home is ideally situated near schools, parks, shops, and restaurants, providing convenience at your doorstep.
